          "value": "<p>The catoblepas breathes a @Template[type:cone|distance:60] of horrid fumes, dealing [[/r {13d6}[poison]]]{13d6 poison damage} (@Check[type:fortitude|dc:32|basic:true] save). The area of this cone is reduced to 30 feet underwater. Targets that fail their saving throw also become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 1} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 2} on a critical failure).</p>\n<p>The catoblepas can't use its Breath Weapon again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
